es with realistic OCR artifacts and formatting issues. Starting with: Piernik z Śliwkami (Polish dessert with corruption), Brocade Chicken with Mushrooms (reconsidering the name for English main), Żur Żytni (Polish soup with artifacts), Roasted Beet Hummus (English appetizer), Drożdże Sernik (Polish cheesecake), and Miso Glazed Eggplant (English main).\n\nFor the remaining slots, I'll use Bigos Letni and Lavender Honey Cake as narrative-style recipes, then add compound titles like the herb roasted pork variation and the traditional/modern piernik pairing. I need to verify the distribution matches what was requested—5 OCR corruption, 3 narrative, 2 compound—since these are distinct categories. The filenames need careful construction to meet the requirements.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":89326,"cache_read_input_tokens":15568,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":89326},"output_tokens":3,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"34e3cc89-b327-406a-aaab-3cc3ab4ee748","uuid":"2261a63a-47f2-4dc8-89c8-9e2dd350e0cc"}
