{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01XAAVi6mkyMKxFrboR7CTPe","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01XBEkGxN8fMqWduX2sYDzrs","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Miso Glazed Eggplant.generated.22.txt","content":"Miso Glazed Eggplant\n\nThis recipe emerged from a lazy Sunday afternoon in a Tokyo izakaya, where I watched a chef brush glossy miso-butter glaze onto charred eggplant slices. The umami-rich miso melted into the soft flesh, creating a dish that was both savory and subtly sweet. Years later, I reconstructed it from memory, adjusting the balance of miso to sake and butter until it tasted like coming home. Serve this at room temperature or gently warmed—it's equally sublime either way.\n\nIngredients:\n\n4 Japanese eggplants (or 2 Italian eggplants)\n4 tbsp white miso paste\n3 tbsp butter, melted\n2 tbsp sake (or mirin)\n1 tbsp soy sauce\n1 tbsp maple syrup\n2 cloves garlic, minced\n1 tsp fresh ginger, grated\n1 tbsp sesame oil\n2 tsp sesame seeds\n2 green onions, chopped\n1 red chili, thinly sliced\n\nInstructions:\n\n1. Slice eggplants lengthwise into ½-inch slabs.\n2. Brush with sesame oil on both sides, salt lightly.\n3. Heat a grill pan or cast iron over medium-high heat.\n4. Grill eggplant 5-6 minutes per side until softened and caramelized.\n5. Whisk together miso, butter, sake, soy sauce, maple syrup, garlic, and ginger.\n6. Transfer grilled eggplant to a serving platter.\n7. Brush glaze generously over each piece.\n8. Sprinkle sesame seeds and green onions on top.\n9. Garnish with sliced red chili.\n\nServe warm or at room temperature.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":655,"cache_read_input_tokens":108386,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":655},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"34e3cc89-b327-406a-aaab-3cc3ab4ee748","uuid":"fab53ca4-0b41-406d-83ea-ea56e116c8e3"}
