{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01G43LPkHHqaxFg9v9PM8KB5","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01XJQYEv6DnKhRNMQ7gUYWrr","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Lavender Honey Cake.generated.22.txt","content":"Lavender Honey Cake\n\nWalking through a Provence market in late June, I was captivated by bundles of fresh lavender hanging from every stall. The vendor insisted I take a small pouch, saying \"bakers know what to do.\" That evening, I experimented: lavender buds steeped in warm honey, folded into a buttery cake batter with ricotta. The result was perfumed but not floral—delicate, like eating a sweetly scented summer breeze. This cake has become my signature for garden parties and quiet afternoons with tea.\n\nIngredients:\n\n300g flour\n200g butter\n150g honey\n100g ricotta cheese\n3 eggs\n100ml whole milk\n2 tbsp fresh lavender buds (or 1 tbsp dried)\n1 tbsp lavender extract (optional)\n1 tsp baking powder\n1 tsp vanilla extract\nzest of 1 lemon\npinch of sea salt\n\nGlaze:\n100g powdered sugar\n3 tbsp honey\n2 tbsp water\n1 tsp fresh lavender buds\n\nInstructions:\n\n1. Heat honey with 2 tbsp lavender buds over low heat for 5 minutes. Remove from heat, let cool.\n2. Strain out lavender buds. You should have about 150g infused honey.\n3. Cream butter with infused honey until pale and fluffy.\n4. Beat in eggs one at a time, then ricotta.\n5. Fold in milk alternately with flour mixed with baking powder and salt.\n6. Stir in vanilla extract, lemon zest, and lavender extract if using.\n7. Pour into buttered 9-inch round cake pan.\n8. Bake at 175°C for 40-45 minutes until golden and a toothpick comes out clean.\n9. Cool in pan 15 minutes, then turn out onto a wire rack.\n10. For glaze: whisk powdered sugar, honey, and water until pourable. Drizzle over cooled cake. Sprinkle fresh lavender buds on top.\n\nServe at room temperature.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":698,"cache_read_input_tokens":109697,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":698},"output_tokens":2,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"34e3cc89-b327-406a-aaab-3cc3ab4ee748","uuid":"dc261cdc-4725-4e95-b196-3f1e9d41547b"}
